==German==
===Etymology===
Alteration of [[Ampel]], with the prefix ''schw'' stemming from [[schwarz]] "black", the party color of the [[CDU]].
===Noun===
'''Schwampel''' ''f''
# a [[coalition]] in the German [[Bundestag]] consisting of the [[CDU]], [[FDP]], and the Green Party.

